0th.270: Day of the Dead celebration around the corner from Porfiria 'Popi' Guzman's house. Community residents from a variety of organizations and groups have gathered for ten years to celebrate the Day of the Dead procession. Claudia Alvidez is one of the lead organizers. Her phone numbers is 773.732.1395 claudia.alvidez@yahoo.com
